psychiatric disorders. The pharmacological algorithm for attention-deficit/
hyperactivity disorder (ADHD) considers comorbid conditions, such as anxiety 
or depression, contraindications for medications, patient or parent preferences, 
and the required duration of effect throughout the day. Strategies for addressing 
partial or non-response include dose adjustments, changing medications or 
