Introduction (S.V.F. and J.K.B.); Epidemiology (C.A.H. and G.V.P.); Mechanisms/pathophysiology 
(I.B., K.R., M.A.B. and S.V.F.); Diagnosis and screening (M.H.S. and S.C.); Management (J.H.N., 
S.C., A.P., M.H.S., J.K.B., M.A.B., K.R. and C.H.); Quality of life (G.V.P. and A.P.); Outlook (J.K.B. 
and S.V.F.). Aside from the first and last authors, authorship is alphabetical. All authors 
extensively commented on each other’s sections.
